metadata.title: Mushy
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a roughly drawn cartoon-style bird with a yellow outline and a white body. It has large black eyes, a pinkish beak, and a small crest on its head. The bird is positioned on the left side. To the right, there's a black-framed screen displaying a simple red flame-shaped logo. The style is simplistic, with bold outlines and minimal detail.

metadata.title: Mushy Speech
metadata.visionDescription: The image depicts a cartoon-style scene with a yellow bird-like character standing on a wooden stage. The character is holding a microphone and speaking energetically at a podium. The background is blue with scattered yellow stars, creating a whimsical, starry atmosphere. Red and yellow pennant banners hang across the top, and red curtains frame the stage on either side. The character has large, expressive eyes, a small beak, and is drawn in a simplistic, bold style.

metadata.title: mushy touch grass
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a cute, cartoon-style yellow chick sitting on a grassy field adorned with flowers. The chick has large, round eyes and an orange beak. It wears a flower crown made of small white flowers. In one wing, it holds a single red rose, and in the other, a colorful bouquet of various flowers, including yellow, pink, and blue. The background is a blue sky with fluffy white clouds. The overall style is cheerful and vibrant, with a playful and friendly appearance.

metadata.title: Mushy chill
metadata.visionDescription: The image features a cute, cartoon-like yellow bird with large, round eyes and an orange beak, sitting on a pink bean bag. The bird is holding a green drink with a straw in its wings. It has simple, bold outlines and a playful design, contributing to a cheerful and cozy atmosphere. The background is a solid, light beige color, emphasizing the central character.
